
KNOWN ISSUES
============

* wxfalsecolor does not do background images (-p or -ip)


USABILITY
=========

* add menu bar

* split falsecolor options in 'base' and 'advanced' (pop-up)


FEATURES
========

falsecolor2:
------------

* background colour option (limits of psign/pcomb?)


wxfalsecolor:
-------------

* controls for legend placement (update getRGBAt() to honor legend offset)

* 'pcond' feature

* show Lux spot readings as labels on image (left mouse click)

* show Lux average reading over area (click-drag)
